body:
@morrisonlevi I think you just need to  invoke `bazel build -- //tensorflow/tools/pip_package:build_pip_package  --gpu` to have the `--project_name` of the `setup.py` of the package set to tensorflow_gpu:
See:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tools/pip_package/build_pip_package.sh#L57
